aa(lp95
VNow, as mentioned before,
p96
aVone of the reasons I can talk to you about this
p97
aVis because there's no non-disclosure agreement on this case.
p98
aVNow how did that happen?
p99
aVWell during the settlement process, when we received our copy, I struck it.
p100
aVMy attorney said, "Nah, no chance of that working."
p101
aVIt came back signed.
p102
aVNow why? You can call them.
p103
